name: B.I.D. (Boxing Is Dead)
description: Ever get the feeling that a boxing match was rigged? One proof of this was the controversial decision win over Bradley of Pacquiao, we have created a spoof off of the WWE/WWF Wrestling logo to show that Boxing has been rigged and is no longer official. Boxing carved tombstone dated the day of the fight.. and the BUSOG bite mark on the back.. along with BUSOG sleeve and hang tags ! This idea was inspired not only by the results of the fight, but of the tweets of the likes of Snoop Dogg, Justin Timberlake, Diego Cash and many more !

name: Panda SAL New Era Fitted
description:
Worn by Kiyan Anthony (aka Carmelo Anthony's Kid here) ! #KnicksTape

No expense was spared on this 100% wool cap with "BUSOG" in raised embroidery on the front, Panda Sal's iconic pencil over the right ear, and Sal's initials forming his face on the back of the cap.

But the real magic is on the undervisor. Not only is there a red sandwich (the middle part of the visor), the undervisor stands out with a bite mark and teeth and a puffy fill. New Era and Johnny Cupcakes said this is a great idea that they've never ever come up with before.
